Schluter thermostat plugin for Indigo Home Automation

The plugin enables monitoring and control of the Schluter DITRA-HEAT Thermostat from the Indigo Home Automation application.

Requirements:
The username/password for your Schluter account
Supported thermostats:  (so far)
- Schluter DITRA-HEAT E-WIFI Thermostat

